    "Cappadocia",
    "Syria"
  ],
  "macroEvent": "Third Century Crisis",
  "eventLabel": "Shapur I''s three invasions of the Roman East (252-260)",
  "factType": "military-event",
  "questions": [
    "沙普尔一世宣称的 37 座被征服城市的确切清单是否可以与罗马方面的史料对勘？",
    "安条克是否被毁坏还是仅被劫掠？考古证据如何？"
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
